---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Kubernetes Adoption"
  descripcion="Accelerate your Kubernetes adoption with a structured path from Docker Compose to production-grade EKS. GitOps workflows, Helm charts, and observability included."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #0d2f50 100%); padding: 100px 24px 80px;"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #60A5FA; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        Solution · Kubernetes Adoption
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        From containers to production Kubernetes<br />without the six-month
        detour.
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10"
        style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.9);"
      >
        Structured Kubernetes adoption — EKS on AWS or bare metal with kubeadm,
        GitOps delivery via ArgoCD, and observability from the first deployment.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
          style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);"
        >
          Start your K8s journey
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all hover:bg-white/10"
          style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);"
        >
          View case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key points -->
  <section style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">
          A complete Kubernetes platform, not just a cluster
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">
          Running Kubernetes in production requires more than kubectl apply. We
          deliver the full platform layer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {
          [
            {
              title: 'Production-grade cluster provisioning',
              desc: 'EKS on AWS and bare-metal clusters with Terraform and kubeadm — managed node groups, IRSA, private networking, and cluster autoscaler. No ClickOps, no undocumented state.',
              icon: 'M21 7.5l-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0l-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9',
            },
            {
              title: 'GitOps delivery with ArgoCD',
              desc: 'All application deployments driven by Git. ArgoCD watches the repo, applies diffs automatically, and alerts on drift. Rollbacks are a git revert away.',
              icon: 'M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5',
            },
            {
              title: 'Helm chart standardization',
              desc: 'Shared Helm library charts for common workloads. Consistent resource requests/limits, health checks, disruption budgets, and network policies across every service.',
              icon: 'M6 6.878V6a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0118 6v.878m-12 0c.235-.083.487-.128.75-.128h10.5c.263 0 .515.045.75.128m-12 0A2.25 2.25 0 004.5 9v.878m13.5-3A2.25 2.25 0 0119.5 9v.878m0 0a2.246 2.246 0 00-.75-.128H5.25c-.263 0-.515.045-.75.128m15 0A2.25 2.25 0 0121 12v6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18v-6c0-.98.626-1.813 1.5-2.122',
            },
            {
              title: 'Full observability from day one',
              desc: 'Prometheus & Grafana for metrics, Loki for logs, Jaeger for traces. Pre-built dashboards for cluster health, pod saturation, and SLO tracking out of the box.',
              icon: 'M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z',
            },
          ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7"
              style="border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                style="background: #EEF4FF;"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  style="color: #1E6FFF;"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    d={icon}
                  />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #0A2540;">
                {title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
                {desc}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Ready to run Kubernetes in production?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">
        Schedule a 30-minute assessment. We'll review your current container
        setup and outline a realistic path to production Kubernetes.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
        style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,111,255,0.45);"
      >
        Schedule Kubernetes assessment
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          ><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- See it in practice -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8" style="border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="section-label">See it in practice</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-3" style="color: #0A2540;">Two Kubernetes implementations</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-5">
          <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">k8s-on-premise</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: #FEF9C3; color: #854D0E; border: 1px solid #FDE047;">In Development</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">Bare-metal Kubernetes with kubeadm + Vagrant. ArgoCD GitOps, Calico CNI, NGINX Ingress. vagrant up → cluster in ~20 min. Phase 3/18 roadmap.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/projects/k8s-on-premise" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Case study →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/k8s-on-premise" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">k8s-devops-platform</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: #F3F4F6; color: #4B5563; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Reference</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: #64748B;">GitOps reference platform — KinD local dev mirrors production. ArgoCD auto-sync + prune + selfHeal. Helm Charts with per-environment values.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="/projects/k8s-devops-platform" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Case study →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/k8s-devops-platform" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
